## 💰 Saving Money in Paris

To keep your budget tight, focus on self-catering and prioritizing free experiences. Instead of paying €20+ for a single museum entry, spend that money on a picnic in a beautiful park and enjoy the city's atmosphere.

## 🚶‍♀️ Navigating the City

The Metro is your friend, but remember that the best way to experience the *vibe* of Paris is by walking. Grouping your attractions geographically (e.g., Montmartre in the morning, Le Marais in the afternoon) will save you time and transportation costs. Always validate your ticket upon entry!
